Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,基于 opentitles.org 英文字幕翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(注意：本字幕针对2020年动画版视频,\N与旧版本在对话内容和时间轴上略有差异)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,【中文翻译/时间轴】巴蛮子sz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁能帮帮我, 求求你们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Somebody help me, please.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要窒息了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}I'm suffocating!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快点, 有谁能帮帮我...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Quickly! Somebody help me, please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要窒息了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}I'm suffocating!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我, 求求你们!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Help me! Please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那, 但我的弟弟怎么办?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah, but what about me brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我现在有更严重的情况要查, 小姐\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid I've got something\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}more serious to look into first, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个年轻人说的是实情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If this young man's telling the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一个同事已经被谋害了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}a colleague of mine's been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 博士, 这个人有话和你说  - 哦, 是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Doctor, this man wants to talk to you. - Oh, Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这位, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossland 督察, 苏格兰场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Detective Inspector Crossland. Scotland Yard. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我把一切都告诉他了  - 你见过这个人吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I told him everything.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Have you ever seen that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们在变色龙机库发现的那个人!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's the man we found in the Chameleon Tours hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,博士的尸体呢, 在哪儿\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor's body. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他...逃走了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He... escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他的智力远在那些普通人之上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}His intelligence is far above normal beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也在你之上, 估计\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Above YOURS, perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了, 去苏黎世的飞机已经准备起飞了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I must leave. The flight to Zurich is ready to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你就留在这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You will remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么目的?  - 弥补你的无能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- For what purpose? - To atone for your incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,博士必须死, 你必须搞定\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor must die, and you must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 博士, 我们去见总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right then, Doctor, we'll go and see the commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让他听听你的故事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want him to hear your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是, 上一次他并没有太相信\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, he wasn't very impressed with it the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次, 他会相信你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This time, he's gonna believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 如果你觉得\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, if you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 待在这里盯着柜台, 我们不会很久\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, stay here and keep an eye on the kiosk.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We shan't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心你的弟弟, 小姐. 我们会替你找到他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't worry about your brother, Miss.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll find him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个督察以后会很出色的!   - 但他相信我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A fat lot of good that inspector's going to be!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But he believes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 是, 不过那也不代表他肯定会采取什么措施\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, year, but that doesn't mean to say\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he's going to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我得去那个变色龙机库看一遭\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think I'll go and have a look\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}round that Chameleon hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己可不行\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Not by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊, 我觉得要是有位男士陪我去, 肯定会好些\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I suppose it would be better\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if I had a man with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 如果博士没让我盯着这个地方就好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye. If only the Doctor hadn't told me\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to watch this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 你是不是总是按别人的吩咐做事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, do you always do everything you're told?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是, 但是博士信任我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, but the Doctor trusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 这就是你的问题了, 对不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah, that's your trouble, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 待在这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟, 他们最多也只能杀了我, 拜拜\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}After all, they can only murder me. Ta-ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 等等\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计这里也不会有什么情况, 你觉得呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't suppose anything will happen here, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都已经关掉柜台了, 所以不太可能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Since they closed the kiosk, so it's hardly likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们不会耽误很久, 对吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And we won't be long, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这就取决于我们能发现什么. 快走吧, 小子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that depends on what we find. Come on, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么, 你需要我给你带路\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In any case, you need me\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to show you the way there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了, 我接受你发现了一具尸体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, all right.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll accept that you found a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是想知道你从哪里来的, 为什么没有护照\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but I still want to know where you come from\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and why you have no passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 显然这不重要吧?   - 违反法律不可能不重要!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Surely that's unimportant?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- It is not unimportant to break the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,先生, 我觉得我们还是得让他先说说\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sir, I think we'll have to let him\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}tell us in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧, 简短一点  - 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Very well. Make it brief.  Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚去变色龙观光游的机库进行了一番搜索\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have just carried out a search\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of the Chameleon Tours hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个行李箱里面, 我们找到了一个男人的躯体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In a packing case, I found the body of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你没告诉我这个, 博士. 又一个人死了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You never told me that, Doctor.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Another dead man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没死, 他处于一种神志不清的状态, 一种昏迷\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, he was in a stupefied state, a sort of coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个人是谁?   - 我不知道他的名字\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Who's this one?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有种感觉, 他是你的雇员之一\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I have a feeling he's one of your employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢, 真的?  - 事实上, 我觉得他可能就在这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh, indeed?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- In fact, I think he may be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,滑行, 沿南部滑行路, 前往27号起飞跑道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Taxi, following southern taxi way\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for departure runway 27...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道这是什么吗?  - 我觉得它像支钢笔\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Do you know what this is?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- It looks like a fountain pen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,事情并不总是看起来的那样. 小心, 它很危险!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Things are not always what they seem.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Careful! It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙观光游也不像它看起来那样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Tours are not quite what they seem either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And what's your theory?\N那你的理论是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等你听了, 恐怕你不会相信\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid you won't believe it\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}when you hear it....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,首先, Gascoigne 督察被一把射线枪谋杀了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}First, Inspector Gascoigne\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}was murdered with a ray gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一把射线枪?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A ray gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一种在这个地球上还没被研发出来的武器\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A weapon that has not yet\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}been developed on this Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦, 真的吗?   - 你看, 我就知道你不会相信我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh, really!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You see, I knew you wouldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 请耐心点, 先生. 我们在试着理解你说的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, now be patient, sir.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We are trying to understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很好. 然后, 我相信变色龙观光游\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well. Next, I believe Chameleon Tours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只不过是一个幌子, 一个掩护 - 掩护什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- to be merely a front - a cover.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护他们大规模绑架年轻人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}For the mass kidnapping of young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而所有这些都发生在我的机场?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And is all this supposed\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to be taking place in my airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的, 就在当下!   - 这可真够了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes. At this very moment.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- That's quite enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能把这家伙关起来吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can't you take that fellow into custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉, 先生. 但你知道他没有违反任何法律\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I'm very sorry, sir,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but you know he hasn't broken any law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,除非是出入境方面的问题, 那可不是我的职责范围\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}except for this immigration business,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and that's not my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Brian Briggs 是你的职责范围  - 那又是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Brian Briggs IS your responsibility!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个年轻人, 参加了变色龙观光游, 然后消失了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's a young man who went on\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the Chameleon tour and vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,得了, 博士, 等一下. 这一点我们还没有确认\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on Doctor, wait a minute.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We're not certain of that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,四处都找不到他, 也找不到我的两朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, he's nowhere to be found,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and neither are my two friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这在我看来就证实了我的观点——\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}which in mind proves my point:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙观光游是个幌子, 就为了绑架年轻人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Tours are a cover\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for the abducting of young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,敢问他们被带到哪里去了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And just where do you think they're taking them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你看, 从我已经呈现的事实来看\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, in view of the facts that I've already presented
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,射线枪, 这种笔, 以及其它一两个东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the ray gun, this pen,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and one or two other things -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们在对付的人, 不是来自这个星球!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think we're dealing with people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who are not from this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没能回答我的问——你刚才说什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That hardly answers my que...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你看, 我就知道你不信我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You see, I knew you wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这完完全全是胡说八道!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is absolute arrant nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看, 博士, 我觉得应该提供一些证据来支撑这些说法\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, Doctor, I think you ought to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}produce some evidence to support all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 证据? 这支笔怎么说?   - 一只笔! 你管这叫证据?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Evidence? What about this pen?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A pen! Do you call that evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你演示一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll demonstrate it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你介意帮我们一下吗?   - 我没明白\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Would you mind helping us?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能把这个杯子举在面前?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Could you hold this cup out in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许你以前见过这个?   - 没有. 啊!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Perhaps you've seen one of these before?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- No. Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它变成冰了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's turned to ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你管这个叫胡说八道?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you call that arrant nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的妈妈爸爸, 已经安全抵达黑森林了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Dear Mum and Dad.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have arrived safely in the Black Forest."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很快再写给你们, 爱你们的 Tim\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Will write again soon. Love, Tim. "
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸, 我...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Dear Dad, I... "
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的妈妈...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Dear Mum... "
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jami​e!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie! 你看我找到了什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie! Look what I've found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里至少有50张明信片\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There must be 50 postcards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定能让那位督察采取点什么行动了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That should make that inspector do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对, 而且我知道去哪里找他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're right, and I know where to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个勇敢的小姑娘, 现在没时间向你致敬了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're a brave wee lassie.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No time to greet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开! 有什么东西进我眼睛了. 走吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get off! I've got something in me eye. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们往哪儿走?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥的办公室\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The commandant's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 这是你要的变色龙观光游后面的飞机排班表\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, here are the remaining flight schedules\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for Chameleon Tours you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个小装置可真厉害  - 最好让我仔细检查一下, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What a nasty little device.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'd better get that checked over, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况?   - Samantha, 下来这边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What the devil...   - Samantha, down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明信片, 快看!  - 我不会容忍有人乱闯控制室!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Postcards! Look.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I will not have my control room invaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有这些也不行吗?  - 你拿的是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Not even for these?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这是你要求的进一步证据, 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think it's the further evidence\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}you required, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对了...跟我想的一样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes... Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在哪里拿到的?  - 在那个机库的办公室里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where did you get these?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- In the office in that hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白这意味着什么吗?   - 规律已经很明显了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You see what they mean?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- All falling into a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个信封写的寄信地址是德国的某个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This envelope is addressed to somewhere in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有, 德文的版本\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah. "Dem Chameleon Reisen, Freiberg."\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That means Chameleon Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你都在叨叨些什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just what are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧, 他们派发出这些卡片\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You see, they give out these cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,让这些孩子在出发之前就写给他们家里的父母\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and get the kids to write home\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to their parents before they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙观光游的家伙就把这些卡片带上飞机\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Chameleon Tours lot take the cards abroad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们把卡片寄回不列颠\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and THEY post them back to Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,于是父母们就以为他们的孩子已经安全抵达了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}So the parents think the children\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}have arrived safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 你觉得他们身上发生了什么事情?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, what do you think happens to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 不, 这些都只不过是臆测\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, now. This is all mere supposition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 对你来说, 也许吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, to you, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里面其中一个孩子恰巧就是我弟弟\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but one of those kids\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}happens to be my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 先生, 就是这位小姐的弟弟失踪了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, sir. This is the young lady\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}whose brother's missing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你看, 她的确收到了一张她弟弟从罗马寄来的卡片\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and you see, she did get a card from him in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是为什么有谁会绑架这些年轻人呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But why would anyone want\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to abduct these young people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们知道了这个, 我们就不会干坐在这里了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, if we knew that, we wouldn't be sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,督察, 我能跟你说句话吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inspector, can I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这家伙有点不正常吗, 对不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You don't think this fellow's\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}a little unbalanced, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 也许是有点不循规蹈矩, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh maybe a wee bit unorthodox, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟, 到目前为止是他给了我们唯一的线索\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But after all, he's given us\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the only lead we've got so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意, 不如放手让他干\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If you could, just see your way to giving him a free hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让他干?  - 只是四处摸索一下, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A free hand? - Just to poke around a little bit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得安全吗, 让这个家伙在机场乱窜?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think it's safe to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}let the fellow roam around the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以依靠我们来盯着他, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You can rely on us to keep an eye on him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 但记在你的头上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, but on your head be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己会去调查变色龙观光游\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I personally will investigate Chameleon Tours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果发现什么, 也会回报给你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}then I'll report back to you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if I've found out anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但于此同时, 你尽量让一切照常运转, 你明白吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But in the meantime, if you could just keep\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}everything going as normal, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们不想让他们听到任何风吹草动  - 不, 不会\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- We don't want them to get wind of anything.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 我给你在机场12个小时的自由时间, 愿老天帮我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, I'm giving you the freedom\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of the airport for 12 hours, heaven help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等12个小时结束, 我期望你带着点真正的证据回到这里来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}At the end of that time, I shall expect you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}back here with some real facts this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你, 总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you, Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们信了那个博士了吗?   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Did they believe the Doctor?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思?   - 我想他怀疑上我了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What do you mean?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I think he suspects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他朝我打开了我们的一个武器, 迫使我跑开了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He turned one of our own weapons on me.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Forced me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你个笨蛋, 你应该待着不动的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You fool. You should have stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 我们没法知道他到底发现了多少了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, we do not know\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}how much he has discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他发现了我们的秘密任务, 他们也不会相信他的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Even if he has discovered the secret\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of our mission, they won't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这些地球人的脑子想不了那么远\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}These Earth minds cannot stretch that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然, 事实远非他们的智力所能想到, 除了博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Of course, the truth is beyond their\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}intelligence, except for that Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他在那里, 我可以杀了他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I know where he is. I could kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要去, 不过不能让你自己有危险\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're going to, but not at the risk\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of your own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还需要你待在航空控制塔台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We still need you in Air Traffic Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,带上这个, 贴到他身上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Take this. Attach it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等你搞好了, 我就可以用这个激活这个装置\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}When you're ready, I shall\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}activate the mechanism with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就可以一劳永逸解决他  - 很好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- That should put paid to him once and for all.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别耽误\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要他在 Blade 队长回来之前就死了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want him dead before Captain Blade returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,博士...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我给你和你两个朋友做了通行证  - 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I've made out a pass for you and your two friends.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 先生. 有一架变色龙的航班进来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me, sir. There's a Chameleon\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}flight coming in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ADSXL 呼叫盖特威克机场塔台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Alpha Delta Sierra X-ray Lima\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}calling Gatwick Airport Control.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克塔台呼叫ADSXL航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Control to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Alpha Delta Sierra X-ray Lima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克塔台呼叫ADSXL航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Control to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Alpha Delta Sierra X-ray Lima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在告诉你航向\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I will now give you your heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们一天有多少航班?   - 七到八个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- How many flights do they use a day?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们有几架飞机?  - 四架\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- How many planes do they use?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以查到他们的注册号, 如果你需要的话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I could get their registration numbers if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一天八个航班却只有四架飞机, 这正常吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Eight flights a day and only four planes.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,正常, 只要他们周转得快\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. They have a very quick turnaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说, 毕竟他们只有短途航线\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I mean, after all they're only on short haul flights
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的, 都是些旅游胜地, /\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You know, all the holiday centres.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,西班牙, 罗马, 雅典, 黑森林\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Spain, Rome, Athens, the Black Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jean, 冬天的排班表在哪里  - 抱歉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Jean, where's the file on winter schedules.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪个是变色龙的飞机  - 哦, 就那个, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Which is the Chameleon plane?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh that one, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看, 他正在 Dunsfold 左转弯\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, he's turning left at Dunsfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉他在Epsom等待, 直到我给出降落许可\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I shall hold him now over Epsom\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until I can give him landing clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们雷达的有效范围是多少?   - 130英里, 怎么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What's the range of your radar?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- 130 miles. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在想他们的飞机什么时候出现  - 我不清楚, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I wondered when this plane first appeared.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I've no idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们开始呼叫之前我们看不到他们. 我先离开一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We don't notice them until they start to call in.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now excuse me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克塔台呼叫ADSXL航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Gatwick Control\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to Alpha Delta Sierra X-ray Lima.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爬升到一万英尺, 在 Epsom 管制区等待降落许可\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Climb to 10,000 feet and hold in\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Epsom control zone to await landing clearance.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ADSXL航班, 爬升到一万英尺, 就地等待\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Alpha Delta Sierra X-ray Lima.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Climbing to 10,000 feet and holding.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,起飞之后你们可以跟住他们多久?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How long do you hold them after take-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他们离开盖特威克管制区, 我们跟他们就没关系了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Once they've left Gatwick Control Zone,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we've finished with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了, 那就意味着他们可能去任何地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I see. That means they might be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是宁愿浪费你的12个小时四处乱窜吗, 还来打扰我的人?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aren't you rather wasting your 12 hours\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}hanging around here, disturbing my people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我一分钟都没有浪费\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't think I've been wasting a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但你非要我走的话, 我会走. Sam! Jamie!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but I'll go if you insist. Sam! Jamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉  - 没事, 完全是我的错\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Sorry.  - It's all right. It's quite my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以前在什么地方没碰见过你吗?   - 我觉得没有\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Haven't I met you somewhere before?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定有一个替身!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You must have a double!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下, 你是这里的经理吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me, are you the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我负责订票, 有什么可以帮你的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm looking after bookings. Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟经理谈话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'd rather like to speak to the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是位警官  - 我们有麻烦吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'm a police officer.  - Is there some trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想和负责人谈  - 那得找 Blade 机长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'd prefer to speak to the person in charge.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- That's Captain Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚从一个航班返回了, 下一个航班马上又要出发\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's just returned from one flight,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}taking off for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他这会儿真的很忙  - 也许我可以直接去飞机上?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He's rather busy at the moment.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Perhaps I could go out to the plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去看看. 请等一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll have to see about that. Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有个警探要见你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A detective wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他怀疑什么了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Does he suspect anything?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 送他去飞机上吧, 我们来对付他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}All right. Send him over to the plane.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll deal with him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定就是这个房间, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you sure this is the right room, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jamie, 你什么时候见我出过错?   - 真是!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Jamie, have you ever known me to be mistaken?  - Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿, 小心一点  - 什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Hey. Now watch out.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,毒气喷嘴就是从那面墙出来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's the wall the gas nozzles came out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在这里什么也没有了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's nothing here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这很高明, 非常高明\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's clever, very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 好了, 这就变得简单了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, well, it makes life simpler for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看, 我定住的那个人是从这附近出来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, the man I froze came from here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 有可能 - 一堵实墙啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, he would - a solid wall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这堵实墙的某个地方, 有一道门\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Somewhere in that solid wall, there's a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是. 我们还是没有找到 Ben 和 Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, and we still haven't found Ben and Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得他们发生什么事了?   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What do you think's happened to them?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们找到了门, 就能找到他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Perhaps if we find that door, we'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快来, 你找那边, 我找这边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on. You take that end, I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossland 督察这会儿在牵制他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inspector Crossland's keeping them busy at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他用力过猛的话, 他不是他们的对手\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but he'll be no match for them\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if he presses them too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现整架飞机都严格遵守国际航空安全标准\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll find that the whole plane conforms strictly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to the international standards of air safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不会有任何人会投诉我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can't think why anybody would complain about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过有人投诉吗? 我不是来查安全措施的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did I say anyone had complained?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm not enquiring about safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我来查的是一个失踪的男孩, 是你们航班的乘客\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My enquiries are about a missing boy.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A passenger on one of your flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,同时还有我的一个同事, Gascoigne 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And there's also the business of a colleague\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of mine, Detective Inspector Gascoigne,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最后有人看见他也是在你们机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}was last seen in your hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有人相信他已经被害了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's believed to have been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这确实不是一件小事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That is indeed a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我得让你推迟起飞一会儿\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid I'm going to have to ask you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to hold up this flight a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一些问题要问你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}while I ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意来总指挥的办公室吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you mind coming to the commandant's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你得允许我失陪一下, 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If you'll just excuse me for a moment, Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些事情要安排\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have some arrangements to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉, 请  - 对不起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Excuse me, please.  - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Blade 机长!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Captain Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是你, 就不会再移动一步\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I shouldn't move any further if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这把枪在对付你的同事时非常有效, 那位 Gascoigne 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This gun proved remarkably effective\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in dealing with your colleague, Inspector Gascoigne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你杀了他  - 很不幸, 一个失误\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You killed him.  - Unfortunately, an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们地球人活着对我们更有用\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You Earth men are more use to us alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,坐到那里去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sit down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地球人是个非常不错的标本, 你觉得呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This Earth man is a particularly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}fine specimen, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许适合总管他自己  - 的确\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Perhaps the director himself.  - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你俩计划把我怎么样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Whatever you two are planning for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须警告你, 这都在英国法律的长臂管辖内\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I must warn you of the long arm of the British law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它够不到你要去的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't think it will reach where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙航班413呼叫塔台, 请求起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Flight 4-1-3 to Control. Request start-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 你看!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么, 博士!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's that, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给不习惯地球空气的人准备的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}For someone who's not used to the Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很有意思\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊! 一套视频监控设备. 我们来看看能看到什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah! A TV monitor set. Let's see what we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像是个医院\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It looks like a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 这里有点热了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, we're getting warmer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟我上次在这里的情况有点不同\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}which is a change from the last time I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快来, 我们去看看盖特威克机场有没有急救站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on. Let's see if there's\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}a first aid post in Gatwick airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要清理翻乱的东西吗, 博士?   - 不用\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Shall we clear up the mess, Doctor?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找急救站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Let's get along to the first aid post.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 我的背\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 我后背!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请拿一个麦芽糖, 谢谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please take a barley sugar. Thank you.
